-- Sarkozy Has Decided to Let Lauvergeon Complete Areva Term, Le Monde Says
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-07-06T04:41:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-06/sarkozy-has-decided-to-let-lauvergeon-complete-areva-term-le-monde-says.html

          
          
             French President Nicolas Sarkozy has
decided to retain Anne Lauvergeon as head of Areva SA until her
mandate expires at the end of 2011, Le Monde reported on its
website, citing an unidentified person.  
          
          


  


        